The user should create file in the project root named ".env" then paste this code so the website can work correctlly

"MONGO_URI=mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/mihna
JWT_SECRET=mihna-development-secret
PORT=4000"


Before using the source run this in terminal inside the project:

npm install # for installing the necessary dependencies like node_modules
node scripts/mongo-algeria-wilayas.js # for adding willayas
node scripts/mongo-categories.js # for adding jobs types 
node scripts/mongo-seed.js # for adding fake or test data so the user dont start in an empty website

And the user need to have MongoDB Compass to access the database
